{"tid":927182,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陽光海灘沖繩出嫁！李麗珊喊到收唔到聲","createTime":"2018-12-04T03:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T04:52:36.000Z","uid":53524,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6318997ab16cf2d96e9e7dab18976399059c6195","tid":927182,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:57:30.000Z","msg":"香港開電視藝人李麗珊（Lisa）上周六與圈外男友於日本沖繩舉行婚禮。Lisa雖然與男友拍拖不久，但在對的時間遇上對的人，故有「閃婚」的決定，望大家送上祝福。新娘子Lisa表示：「行禮當日，一切都好似睇戲咁，只係自己做主角。因為婚禮由婚禮公司負責，參加婚禮的都是雙方的家人和兄弟姊妹，所以我們心情都好輕鬆，唔會緊張。」<br />\n<br />\n行禮前有進行綵排，以為一切好順利，誰知行禮時，Lisa翹住爸爸慢慢步入教堂，她說：「喺爸爸將我隻手交畀未婚夫嗰一刻，見到爸爸雙眼通紅，眼淚快流出來。我即時『中箭』，眼淚鼻水一齊流出來&hellip;&hellip;嗰一刻可以話係人生中最感動嘅畫面，眼淚自動流下來，強忍都搞唔掂。」"},{"pid":"b461eb1c970311eb859dd6ee7100992173470e57","tid":927182,"uid":191815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:59:30.000Z","msg":"仔都生咗兩件<br />\n咪玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1400005430828b12f697087da61ed323ac8ebb84","tid":927182,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:02:30.000Z","msg":"滑浪嗰個？"},{"pid":"ccb69aa6d6975049d43ecd13e0ebef7a3a9cee20","tid":927182,"uid":65774,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:14:26.000Z","msg":"滑浪果個係李珊珊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4625f65cc03c335a7d2b7735a05b3b046daf98","tid":927182,"uid":146435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b461eb1c970311eb859dd6ee7100992173470e57","tid":927182,"uid":191815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:59:30.000Z","msg":"仔都生咗兩件<br />\n咪玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:14:55.000Z","msg":"4百萬一件"},{"pid":"b44cbd57555ad7975cc0ba9fecbd1fae4601689f","tid":927182,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"腦cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"h